Summary: it was a burnt orange color
divs: Sighting DetailsI WAS OUTSIDE HAVING A SMOKE AND I LOOKED UP AND SAW 2 JETS FLYING FROM THE SE TO NW I LOOKED OUT AHEAD OF THEM AND SAW A CIRCULAR OBJECT BURNT ORANGE IN COLOR NOT BLINKING BUT A SOLID COLOR IT WAS FLYING AWAY FROM THE JETS I SOON REALIZED THAT THEY WERE CHASING THIS OBJECT AFTER ABOUT 3 MINUETS THE LEAD JET CAUGHT UP TO THE OBJECT AND AT THAT TIME THE OBJECT DISSAPPERED IDONT KNOW WHAT HAPPENED TO IT IT WAS VERY STRANGE IT WAS THERE ONE SECOND AND GONE THE NEXT THE 2 JETS CONITUNIED ON THE NW AND DISSAPPEARED
